{
  "texts": [
    "Then we have that",
    "where the inequality above comes from the positive definiteness of S, i.e., S i,i = e ⊤ i Se i ≥ λ min, ∀i.",
    "Let A ∈ R m×n be a matrix with full column rank and B ∈ R n×p be a non-zero matrix.",
    "Let σ min (•) be the smallest non-zero singular value.",
    "Then it holds that σ min (AB) ≥ σ min (A)σ min (B)."
  ]
}